              "Severe pain or rapidly worsening blister",
              "Large burn blister, chemical/electrical burn, or burn over a joint/face/hands/genitals",
              "Blisters near eyes, mouth, or genitals",
              "Widespread blistering, peeling skin, or medication-related rash",
